    • Class com.aventstack.extentreports.model.Test extends Object implements Serializable

      serialVersionUID:
      5590943223572254960L

      • Serialized Fields

        • level

          int level
          Level describes the hierarchy of the test in the tree. A level 0 indicates a parent test. Level 1 indicates an immediate child of the parent, level 2 indicates an immediate child of the Child and so on.. The bottom-most test in the hierarchy is considered a leaf

        • testId

          int testId
          A unique ID, generated by AtomicInteger

        • parent

          Test parent
          If this Test is at the top-most level, or in other words, has a level value of 0, parent will be null. This field will only contain a value if the Test is a child, or has a level 1 or greater.

        • status

          Status status
          Status of this test, defaults to PASS

        • node

          AbstractStructure<T> node
          A structure containing all nodes of this test

        • log

          AbstractStructure<T> log
          A structure containing all logs/events of this test

        • category

          AbstractStructure<T> category
          A structure containing all categories assigned to this test

        • author

          AbstractStructure<T> author
          A structure containing all authors assigned to this test

        • device

          AbstractStructure<T> device
          A structure containing all devices assigned to this test

        • startTime

          Date startTime
          Time the test was started

        • endTime

          Date endTime
          Time the test was ended

        • mongoId

          org.bson.types.ObjectId mongoId
          An assigned ObjectId

        • bddType

          Class<T> bddType
          Type of BDD object represented by IGherkinFormatterModel. It can have one of the following values:
          • Feature
          • Background
          • Scenario
          • Given
          • When
          • Then
          • And

        • name

          String name
          Name of the test

        • hierarchicalName

          String hierarchicalName
          Hierarchical name of the test

          Note: This field will equal the name if the test is the top-most level.

          For tests having level 1 or greater, the hierarchical name would be separated by a dot character as: Test.Child.GrandChild

        • description

          String description
          Description

        • ended

          boolean ended
          Indicates if the test has ended

        • usesManualConfiguration

          boolean usesManualConfiguration
          This setting allows setting test with your own time-stamps. With this enabled, Extent does not use time-stamps for tests at the time they were created
